---
title: Moroccan Lamb & Spinach Jewelled Couscous with Currants & Yoghurt
description: Dreaming of warm Moroccan nights? Try our lamb and jewelled couscous, bursting with rich flavours, currants, spinach and
almonds. This dish is sure to transport you from the dinner table to Morocco on the very first bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
